latestPosts.caption:
From red flag to the one - Maiti & Mushand’s love story is 17 years in the making! 💘 What started with friendship (and a little hesitation) led to a Parisian proposal in front of the Eiffel Tower🤩

But let’s be real - Maiti knew all along this was meant to be🫶🏼🥹 Watch their beautiful journey unfold on Nykaa Wali Shaadi, Episode 2, streaming tonight on @officialjiocinema!

#NykaaWaliShaadi #Nykaa

Before the big glam moment comes the big glow moment! ✨

Right before stepping into @makeupbyriddhima’s chair, our Nykaa Wali Bride, Maiti, prepped her skin with the super-nourishing Lancome Advanced Genifique Serum - because nothing says main character energy like radiant, nourished skin! And with its 3D applicator, it’s practically a mini spa moment before the shaadi madness.

Watch her bridal transformation unfold on Nykaa Wali Shaadi, streaming now on @officialjiocinema! 

#NykaaWaliShaadi #Nykaa

Crafted in luxurious satin organza, the lehenga features delicate, hand-embroidered floral motifs, blending classic design with contemporary flair.

The intricate embroidery, adorned with glass beads, pearls, and sequins, brings the design to life, creating an ethereal effect. 

Mushand in a Gold Sherwani set paired with Silk pants & a Monga Silk dupatta, crafted using raw Silk with cord detailing in a luxurious yet subtle detail made using cord detailing can elevate the overall design with intricate patterns, making it sophisticated and regal.

The lehenga is made in a, romantic pink, crafted from luxurious satin organza. The delicate fabric drapes beautifully, giving it an ethereal, almost weightless feel. 

The shimmering pearls catch the light with every movement, while the sequins and beads create a mesmerizing sparkle, bringing the entire ensemble to life. The glass elements add a touch of opulence, making it the perfect balance of elegance and grandeur. 

It’s a piece that not only reflects timeless beauty but also feels like a celebration of joy and love.

latestPosts.caption:
Crafted in luxurious satin organza, the lehenga features delicate, hand-embroidered, floral motifs, blending classic design with contemporary flair.

The intricate embroidery, adorned with glass beads, pearls, and sequins, brings the design to life, creating an ethereal effect. 

What makes this lehenga even more special is the time and effort that went into its creation. With over 1,500 man-hours dedicated to perfecting every stitch, each embellishment is thoughtfully placed to highlight the beauty of the fabric and the intricate design. 

It’s not just a garment; it’s one that represents my vision, passion, and the careful craftsmanship that went into bringing it to life for the most important day of my life. - Maiti Shahani
